# Compiled binaries (no extension, same name as the .c file)
# Each program builds a binary with the same basename in its folder.
# Ignore all of them so they never get committed.

# Pattern: any file in a subfolder that has no extension and is executable
# is a build artifact. We list them explicitly to be safe.

